'''201 North Charles Street Building''' is a [[high-rise]] office building located at 201 North Charles Street in [[Baltimore, Maryland|Baltimore]], [[Maryland]]. The building rises 28 [[Storey|floors]] and {{convert|350|ft|m|0}} in height,<ref name="EMP"/> and is tied with [[Charles Center|Charles Towers North Apartments]] as the 13th-tallest building in the city. The structure was completed in 1967, and is an example of [[International style (architecture)|international architecture]].<ref name="SKY"/>
